flowchart TD
    A[Student submits Group Creation Request] --> B{Is request valid?}
    B -->|Yes| C[Create GroupCreationRequest object]
    B -->|No| Z[Return error to student]

    C --> D[Create GroupMemberApproval for creator]
    D --> E[Create GroupMemberApproval for invited students]
    E --> F[Create notifications for all invitees]

    F --> G{Do all members approve?}
    G -->|Yes| H[Finalize Group creation]
    G -->|No| I[Wait for responses]

    H --> J[Group object created with members and supervisors]
    J --> K[Notify all members: Group ready]
    I --> L[Pending approvals]
